response.original_title: KidSuper AW25 “FROM A PLACE I HAVE NEVER BEEN” Paris Fashion Week
response.overview: KidSuper’s AW25 From a Place I Have Never Been turns the runway into a surreal performance, with wind sculptures swirling around sculptural, introspective looks. Colm Dillane blends playful prints with muted tones and avant-garde shapes, like a coat that becomes a hammock. Collaborations with BAPE and WILDSIDE Yohji Yamamoto anchor the show in boundary-pushing creativity.
